item.title: CVE-2020-5634|2024-08-04T08:39:25.452Z -- elecom%20co.%2Cltd. -- elecom%20lan%20routers
item.description: ELECOM LAN routers (WRC-2533GST2 firmware versions prior to v1.14, WRC-1900GST2 firmware versions prior to v1.14, WRC-1750GST2 firmware versions prior to v1.14, and WRC-1167GST2 firmware versions prior to v1.10) allow an attacker on the same network segment to execute arbitrary OS commands with a root privilege via unspecified vectors.
